quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,34,"Ko haɗata ɓe nde Alla leptataa ɓe, hara kamɓe hiɓe sakkaade Juulirde hormante nden? Ɓe wonaali heftuɓe nde. Heftuɓe Mo wonaali si wanaa ɓen gomɗumɓe, kono ɓurɓe ɗuuɗude e maɓɓe anndaa"
  8,35,"Julde maɓɓe nden ka Suudu wonaali, si wanaa wuuɗugol e kellugol : \"Meeɗiree lepte ɗen sabu ko yeddiraynoɗon kon"
  8,36,"Pellet, ɓen yedduɓe, hiɓe nafqira jawle maɓɓe ɗen no ɓe sakkora (yimɓe ɓen) e laawol Alla ngol. Maa ɓe nafqu ɗe, refti wontana ɓe ninse, refti ɓe foolee. Ɓen yedduɓe non, ko ka Jahannama ɓe mooɓoytee"
  8,37,"Fii yo Alla senndindir soɓe ɗen e ko laaɓi kon, O waɗa soɓe ɗen yoga mun e dow yoga, O fawindira ɗum fow O waɗta ɗum ka nder Jahamma. ko ɓen ɗon woni hayruɓe ɓen"
  8,38,"Maakan ɓen yedduɓe: si ɓe haɗitike; ɓe haforante ko yawti. Si ɓe fillitike, haray gomɗii laawol adinooɓe ɓen yawtii"
  8,39,"Haɓee ɓe haa ka tawata fitina laatotaako, diina kan fow laatanoo Alla. Si ɓe haɗitike, haray pellet, Alla ko reenuɗo ko ɓe golla kon"
  8,40,"Si ɓe huccitii, anndee pellet, ko Alla woni Giɗo mon. O yooɗii Giɗo O yooɗii Ballo"